docs {
  ## Remove Credit Note Comment Attachment
  ลบไฟล์แนบเดี่ยวออกจากคอมเมนต์ ผ่าน fileToken

  Removes a single attachment from a credit note comment by its file token.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Comment ID |
  | `fileToken` | string | File token of the attachment to remove |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `procurement.credit_note:update`
  - **Roles**: Purchase

  > To remove multiple files or combine with adding new files, use `04 - Update` (PATCH) which supports `attachments: { add, remove }` in multipart form.

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
  | 403 | User lacks `procurement.credit_note:update` permission |
  | 404 | Comment or attachment not found |
}
